en_644370_0	One more phase of the Lakviru Meditation project, conducted by Ven Diyasenpura Wimala Thero of the Bawunseth Meditation Centre at Helummahara, Dekatana got underway on Monday (9) for 28 Army personnel.
en_644370_1	This meditation practice programme, organized by the Directorate of Psychological Operations focused on promotion of mental stability of Army personnel.
